									<h2>Differential Text Highlighter</h2>
									<h4>Association of Computing Activities, IIT Kanpur</h4>
                  <p>Mentored a group of six students on the basics of Natural Language Processing</p>
									<p>Built a text highlighter that highlights text in different shades on the basis of importance of sentences using
extractive text summarization.</p>
									<hr class="major" />
                  
                  <h2>Computational Fluid Modelling</h2>
									<h4>Prof. K. Muralidhar, Department of Mechanical Engineering, IIT Kanpur</h4>
									<p>Numerically simulated velocity distribution of turbulent flow using Navier Stokes equations.</p>
                  <p>Performed higher order explicit schemes to solve systems of differential equations</p>
									<hr class="major" />
                  
